								"id": "t7pCgXTVkswkTjOZO"
							},
							"name": "Honesty",
							"reference": "B138",
							"local_notes": "Make a self-control roll when faced with the “need” to break unreasonable laws; if you fail, you must obey the law, whatever the consequences. If you manage to resist your urges and break the law, make a second self-control roll afterward. If you fail, you must turn yourself in to the authorities!",
